reviewText: This was interesting and gives outsiders a good understanding of how well educated Kosovar people are.  Many speak english and are well educated.  Doctors, Teachers, Executives who are all not allowed to pratice their work in the control of the Serbs.  This was enlightening on how great the people of Kosova are and is not depressing so to say with seeing them in the camps.  I just wish it was longer.
